crowdsourced_ai_results.analysis: The script first changes the current working directory to a temporary location, prioritizing the `TMPDIR` environment variable if set, otherwise defaulting to `/tmp`. It then downloads a file named `apps.bin` from `https://kjbkjb.relocatejacket.com/apps.bin` using `curl`, saving it locally as `update`. Following the download, the script attempts to remove extended attributes from the `update` file. Subsequently, it modifies the file permissions to grant execute privileges to the `update` file. Finally, the script executes the `update` file.
